{
  "document_id": "sir-28",
  "title": "Sirach 28",
  "type": "scripture",
  "translation": "NRSVue",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-1",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 1,
      "text": "The vengeful will face the Lord’s vengeance,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-2",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 2,
      "text": "Forgive your neighbor the wrong he has done,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-3",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 3,
      "text": "Does anyone harbor anger against another"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-4",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 4,
      "text": "If people have no mercy toward those like themselves,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-5",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 5,
      "text": "If mere mortals harbor wrath,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-6",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 6,
      "text": "Remember the end of your life and set enmity aside;"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-7",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 7,
      "text": "Remember the commandments and do not be angry with your neighbor;"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-8",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 8,
      "text": "Refrain from strife, and your sins will be fewer,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-9",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 9,
      "text": "and the sinner disrupts friendships"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-10",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 10,
      "text": "In proportion to the fuel, so will the fire burn,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-11",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 11,
      "text": "A hasty quarrel kindles a fire,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-12",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 12,
      "text": "If you blow on a spark, it will glow;"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-13",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 13,
      "text": "Curse the gossips and the double-tongued,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-14",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 14,
      "text": "Slander has shaken many"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-15",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 15,
      "text": "Slander has driven courageous women from their homes"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-16",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 16,
      "text": "Those who pay heed to slander will not find rest,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-17",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 17,
      "text": "The blow of a whip raises a welt,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-18",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 18,
      "text": "Many have fallen by the edge of the sword,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-19",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 19,
      "text": "Happy is the one who is protected from it,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-20",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 20,
      "text": "For its yoke is a yoke of iron,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-21",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 21,
      "text": "its death is an evil death,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-22",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 22,
      "text": "It has no power over the godly;"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-23",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 23,
      "text": "Those who forsake the Lord will fall into its power;"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-24",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 24,
      "text": "Look! Fence in your property with thorns,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-25",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 25,
      "text": "and make balances and scales for your words."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "sir-28-26",
      "type": "verse",
      "number": 26,
      "text": "Take care not to err with your tongue"
    }
  ]
}